{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act41side", "eventName": "輓歌燃燒殆盡", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "EA-3", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "惶惑與衝動", "storyInfo": "慶功會上，因貪欲而陷入癲狂的深池被貪婪的紅龍引入黑林。另一邊，拉芙希妮和布莉吉從糧店老闆的口中得知了提奧失蹤的真相與走私糧車的去向。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g2_citystreets_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ghosthunter_intro", "key": "$ghosthunter_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_insectfly", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一隻甲蟲低低飛過黑暗瀰漫的街巷。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠奮力振翅，卻僅僅只是闖進了一片幾乎無人踏足的廢棄街區。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "純金製的身軀太重，翅膀上的寶石也對飛翔無益，牠飛了短短一點距離就不得不趴在石板中間的縫隙處休息——"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_246", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-80,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你再跑啊！", "name": "“官僚”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_246"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抓住了，抓住了！", "name": "“官僚”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_246"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crowdtalk_fear", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抓住你那隻爛蟲之後就快點去幫我撿水晶！快滾到陰溝裡了！", "name": "“酷吏”"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我現在就過去——", "name": "“官僚”"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對，如果我幫你撿了，你是不是要分點什麼給我？", "name": "“官僚”"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "分，分！你先來幫我撿！水晶滾進陰溝裡，你難道不心痛嗎？", "name": "“酷吏”"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，我的好雲獸，現在你是我的了！", "name": "“拷問者”"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劍上的寶石……還好，還好，一個都沒掉……", "name": "“監察官”"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“校官”他們呢？", "name": "“拷問者”"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "管他們幹嘛？", "name": "“官僚”"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "官僚把蛀蟲藏進懷裡，酷吏不厭其煩地看著淚滴一次又一次滑落。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拷問者粗魯地擺布雲獸的肢體，監察官舉起那柄劍，彷彿手執生殺的權力……"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "stopSound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……呵，真熱鬧啊。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$2"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然可以把這些財寶賜給你們，我的僕臣們。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$2"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們喜歡這些東西到這種地步，要是不滿足你們，不解風情的反而是我了。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$2"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我把這些給你們之後，你們又想從我手中拿走什麼呢？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$2"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我猜猜……", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#6$2"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "59_i03", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"yFrom": 70.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.4, "yScaleFrom": 1.4, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 25.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知為何，原本走到盡頭的小巷中憑空出現一條路，更多璀璨奪目的東西朝著路的深處湧去。"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們已經無暇撫弄手裡的東西了。"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們撿起地上的財寶，塞進口袋或是背在身上，連腰都來不及挺直就奔向下一個閃閃發光的地方。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有人關心這條路通往何方。"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "", "name": "官僚"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……明天我就去多索雷斯，賣了那麼多貨，早就該幫自己買一點東西了……", "name": "官僚"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……納斯爾紗這群鄉巴佬，應該再榨一些他們身上的油水出來……", "name": "酷吏"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……別忘了分我一些……", "name": "監察官"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……等城裡人真的把“維多利亞間諜”送到我這裡來……", "name": "拷問者"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，聽聽，你們貪圖的何止是財寶啊。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "優渥的生活、高貴的地位、橫流的物慾、生殺的權柄……你們都想要。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不討厭忠於自己慾望的人，你們要的東西，送人也沒什麼可惜。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而唯一不巧的是，你們是我的僕臣，而你們似乎比我還貪婪不少。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……再見，去你們該去的地方吧。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "財寶於無路處憑空鋪成一條閃閃發光的路，送徹底癲狂的人群走出巢穴，走上大地……"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走向黑暗的來處，那殘忍地張開大口的黑林。"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "type": "cg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "type": "cg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutryinside", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這一段，和您之前講的東西，風格完全不同。", "name": "神秘的女性"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我早就說過，觀察、靈感、寫作過程中捨棄的部分，我會一股腦拋出來。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#6$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我真的能將這個故事完完整整地用統一的風格講完，那我也不用在這裡喝臭酸的啤酒了。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#6$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "非要給故事一個結局的人是你，不是我。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確如此。", "name": "神秘的女性"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，如果我非要把這一段當成您的創作，是不是可以說，前面那位布莉吉小姐被黑霧拒絕也算是創作？", "name": "神秘的女性"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……至少不會比你硬塞到故事裡的“放逐王”更“創作”。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#7$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#7$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，接下來您要講的到底是觀察，還是創作呢？", "name": "神秘的女性"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你願意就自己去區分。你到底想不想讓我繼續講？", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#5$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，當然……", "name": "神秘的女性"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g10_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 1.5, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.7, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾瑪她到底怎麼了？", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是輕微的營養不良，外加受了風寒。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在黑林外面的時候看起來沒有病得這麼重啊。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……很有可能是心病。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打造雕像的鐵要挨家挨戶收集，人們為了節省燃料連燈都不願意開，更別說食物了……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她能押什麼東西出去？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是糧店老闆，所以……？", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她也只是個糧店老闆，一個人不可能做到這些。八成有人指使她。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#7$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還有提奧的事要問，沒時間等她自己醒過來了。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#7$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃——啊！", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾瑪，你醒了？", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#6$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尼亞——尼亞爾！", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你帶我走吧……你帶我走吧！", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，她還沒醒。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她好像在喊一個人的名字……尼亞爾？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“尼亞爾”……有這個署名給她寄過信，應該是親近的人吧。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個人現在在哪裡？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道，但這個人有段時間沒寄信給艾瑪了。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#10$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尼亞爾……", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你罵我吧，打我也可以，只是別丟下我不管……", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“官僚”讓我運糧食，我就運……你死在戰場上，我活著又有什麼意義？我對別人好，又能怎麼樣？", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“官僚”……是深池的人。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#7$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正城裡那麼多糧食，就運一批，不會有事的……", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正城裡的糧食已經沒有了，就算這一批運出去，也不會有事的……", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會有事的……", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們……還要叫醒她嗎？", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#10$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再等等。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……為什麼活下來的不是你？", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼……為什麼該死的維多利亞人……他們的孩子能活下來？", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞人的……孩子？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#11$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……為什麼……", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……啊——", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，親愛的——我會糾正它——", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等著我，尼亞爾……等著我，親愛的！", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚……", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗚……嗚！", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我見不到你了，親愛的！我見不到你……", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼，為什麼？！", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殺死你的維多利亞人，他們已經被趕走了！", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連最後那個維多利亞壞種，也已經在我眼前……死掉了……", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尼亞爾……", "name": "擔憂的居民"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾瑪滾燙的額頭上滿是汗珠，連綿惡夢讓她無意識地抓住身下的床單，渾身止不住地顫抖著。"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而房間裡的另外兩個人同時站了起來。"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g2_citystreets_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宵禁已經開始一段時間了，我們現在真的能自由行動嗎？", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我帶著你。如果黑霧真的要吞噬我們之中的任何一個，就讓它來試試看。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，堡壘那邊有人走過來了！", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#8$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#11$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像是深池的人，是……", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#8$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“校官”先生！", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#6$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他怎麼了？一副魂不守舍的樣子……", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“校官”！！", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#4$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰？！", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#4$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮小姐？", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#4$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮小姐，現在，回到……", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“校官”先生，發生什麼事了？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#11$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今晚沒有任何事發生。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“校官”先生，城中糧荒的事情已經有線索了。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這間糧店的老闆艾瑪受“官僚”指使，一直偷偷把糧食運出納斯爾紗走私。如果動作夠快，我們還能把糧食追回來。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是“官僚”？我早該想到是他——", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#5$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是太晚了，一切都太晚了。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼太晚了？難道你知道糧食的下落了？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#11$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "校官", "content": "不是糧食，而是……"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "校官", "content": "我。我們。"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮小姐，感謝您的消息，但我……", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“校官”先生，到底發生什麼事了？告訴我！", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#7$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，今晚沒有任何事發生。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我不知道到底出了什麼事，才能讓你這樣的人，為了一個理想不惜奪走那麼多人生命的……戰士，變成現在這個樣子。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#7$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你和深池，你們踩著那麼多人的屍骸建立這個國度，就是為了把自己的同胞困在城中餓死嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#7$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，拉芙希妮小姐，絕不。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多謝您的消息，我……我會自己去解決這個問題。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，以後別再提起深池這個詞。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，既然我已經答應您，今晚請您無論如何都不要再踏上街道一步，更不要像現在這樣，帶著無關緊要的人破壞宵禁。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這都是為了你們好。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "o"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "o", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮還想說些什麼，校官卻不想再回應。"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他轉了個身，拖著沉重的步伐，往城外的方向走去。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們真的要像他說的一樣躲起來嗎？", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不，提奧的事應該立刻告訴涅梅絲。你知道她住哪裡嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離這裡有點遠，幾乎在整個納斯爾紗的另一邊。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#10$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們現在就過去。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g2_citystreets_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲家就在前面。", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#10$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一路順利，看來今晚霧氣沒有滲進城裡……", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#10$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲，你在家嗎？", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#10$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲？", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，涅梅絲不是說她晚上要參加深池的慶功會嗎？難道她還沒回來？", "name": "布莉吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4177_brigid_1#11$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“校官”剛剛是從堡壘的方向往外走，慶功會應該結束了才對……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮小姐……布莉吉？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮正想開口，忽然對上了涅梅絲的眼睛。"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的雙眼甚至比剛剛的校官更加無神。"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1694_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲，到底怎麼了，難道慶功會上出了什麼事？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1694_1#11$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，今天晚上沒有任何事情發生……", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，你們怎麼在這裡？！", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快，快進屋！今晚千萬別在街上逗留！", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g8_blackforest_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_blacksmoke_01", "fade": "true", "fadetime": 0.5, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在涅梅絲手忙腳亂地拉著拉芙希妮和布莉吉進屋的時候，校官已經走出了納斯爾紗。"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他走入林中，走向黑暗，一直走進黑霧的最深處。"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_blacksmoke_02", "fade": "true", "fadetime": 3.0, "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"layer": 1.0, "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g9_blackforest_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_carriage_loop", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "ca"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "ca", "fadetime": 5.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "片刻之後，先前被運出納斯爾紗的糧食從黑林中緩緩現出形跡。"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們將在天亮前回到納斯爾紗的農業地塊。"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g1_citystreets_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "糧荒在天亮後得到了一定程度的緩解，校官卻沒有從黑林中回來——不過也沒有人關心這件事情。"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些奇蹟般地出現在農業地塊並流向各街糧店的糧食，離真正解決問題所需的數量仍差得很遠。"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而那一夜後便再也沒有回來的人，其實遠遠不只那位校官，儘管城裡的人還不知情。"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，太陽無情地再次升到正空之上。"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅龍和離群的守靈人走上街頭，震驚地看著那些已成常態的廝打與攻訐逐漸演化成更激烈的傷害。"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遊牧人敲響了鐵匠的門，她正要為他帶來一個不幸的消息。"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}